Thank you for choosing Math Practice Games!, an educational iOS game application. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your data. By using Math Practice Games!, you consent to the practices described in this policy.

1. Information We Collect

1.1. Personal Information: Math Practice Games! does not collect or store any personally identifiable information (PII) from users, especially children under the age of 13, without explicit parental consent.

1.2. Non-Personal Information: We may collect non-personal information, including:

    Device Information: We may collect device information such as device type, operating system, and unique device identifiers for the purpose of improving app performance and user experience.

    Usage Data: We may collect data on how you interact with the app, including the duration of gameplay, scores, and statistics, to enhance our services and understand user behavior better.

2. How We Use Your Information

    Improving the App: We use non-personal information to analyze app usage and performance, enabling us to make improvements and optimize the user experience.

3. Disclosure of Information

    Third Parties: We do not share any personal or non-personal information with third parties for marketing or advertising purposes.

4. Parental Consent and Control

    Parental Consent: If a user is under the age of 13, we require parental consent for the collection and use of any personal information. Parents or guardians can contact us at [contact email] to provide or withdraw consent.

    Parental Controls: Parents can access, change, or delete their child's personal information or account data by contacting us at [contact email]. Parents can also review their child's progress and game statistics within the app.

5. Data Security

    We take reasonable measures to protect the security and confidentiality of your information. However, no method of transmission or storage is completely secure. While we strive to protect your data, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

6. Updates to this Privacy Policy

    We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes to our information practices. We will notify you of any significant changes through the app or via email.

7. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or the data we collect, please contact us at:

xtvwerf13@gmail.com

We take your privacy seriously and will respond to inquiries promptly.

By using Math Practice Games!, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy. Please review this policy periodically for updates.
